        "release_date": "1980-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "description": "The Modified Bed Bath VR Simulator app immerses Certified Nursing Assistant (CNA) trainees in a virtual environment where they can practice and master the skills required for providing a proper modified bed bath. This application guides users through each step of the process, including preparing supplies, maintaining patient privacy, and ensuring thorough and gentle cleaning.  \n\n# Learning Objectives:  \n- Remembering the steps and protocols for giving a modified bed bath  \n- Understanding the importance of hygiene and patient comfort \n- Applying the correct techniques for bathing different parts of the body \n- Analyzing the patient's condition to ensure no areas are missed \n- Creating a supportive and respectful environment for patients during the bathing process.  \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to perform modified bed baths effectively and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ",
